    "The diminished performance in configurations without these components underscores their importance in enhancing model reasoning ability.",
    "This paper introduced the Explanation-Guided LLMs Active Distillation (ELAD) framework to address the challenges of deploying LLMs due to the high memory and computational demands.",
    "Our proposed framework achieves LLMs active distillation with explanation-guided sample selection and a customized LLM-annotated explanation revision.",
    "Extensive experiments on various reasoning datasets demonstrate the effectiveness of our approach in enhancing the distillation efficiency.",
    "Our method, which utilizes LLMs as agents in active learning, is influenced by the design of prompts for the LLM, potentially affecting the quality of generated explanations and answers."
